sequenceDiagram
    actor Learner
    participant ExtLMS as External LMS (Canvas etc.)
    participant SetFlow as SetFlow (/api/lti/*)
    participant DB as Database (central)
    participant JWKS as LMS JWKS Endpoint

    Note over Learner,JWKS: Phase 0 — Admin Registration (one-time setup)
    Note over DB: Admin registers platform in /dashboard/admin/lti<br/>INSERT Lti13Platform { issuer, clientId, authLoginUrl, jwksUrl, tokenUrl }<br/>INSERT LtiToolKey { RSA keypair, rotatedAt }

    Note over Learner,JWKS: Phase 1 — Login Initiation (every launch)

    Learner->>ExtLMS: Clicks SetFlow tool link
    ExtLMS->>SetFlow: GET /api/lti/login-init<br/>iss= · login_hint= · target_link_uri=
    SetFlow->>DB: Lookup Lti13Platform by issuer (iss)
    DB-->>SetFlow: Platform config { authLoginUrl, clientId }
    SetFlow->>SetFlow: buildAuthRedirect()<br/>Generate nonce (store in session/cookie)<br/>Build OIDC params (response_type=id_token)
    SetFlow-->>ExtLMS: 302 Redirect to platform authLoginUrl<br/>?response_type=id_token&client_id=...&nonce=...

    Note over Learner,JWKS: Phase 2 — OIDC Auth + Token Delivery

    ExtLMS->>ExtLMS: Platform authenticates learner<br/>Builds LTI claims JWT
    ExtLMS->>SetFlow: POST /api/lti/launch<br/>id_token= (signed JWT, form_post)
    Note over SetFlow: Origin/Referer check (lti-origin-check.ts)<br/>Must come from registered login URL

    SetFlow->>JWKS: Fetch platform public keys<br/>createRemoteJWKSet(platform.jwksUrl)
    JWKS-->>SetFlow: JWK Set (cached)
    SetFlow->>SetFlow: verifyIdToken()<br/>1. Verify signature (RS256 via JWKS)<br/>2. Check issuer matches registered platform<br/>3. Check audience = clientId<br/>4. Verify nonce (replay protection)<br/>5. Check expiry (exp claim)<br/>6. Confirm LTI version = 1.3.x

    alt Verification fails
        SetFlow-->>Learner: 401 Invalid LTI launch
    end

    SetFlow->>SetFlow: Extract LTI claims<br/>roles · context · resourceLink · deployment<br/>ltiRolesToUserRole() → UserRole

    SetFlow->>DB: Find or create User (by email from claims)<br/>Set User.orgId if tenantId in platform config<br/>Create OrgMember row if new affiliation
    DB-->>SetFlow: User session established

    SetFlow->>SetFlow: Set sf-lti-launched cookie<br/>(HttpOnly · Secure · Partitioned · CHIPS)
    Note over SetFlow: Relax CSP frame-ancestors to:<br/>'self' + platform origin<br/>Only for LTI_IFRAMABLE_PATHS

    SetFlow-->>ExtLMS: 302 → target_link_uri (SetFlow page)
    ExtLMS-->>Learner: SetFlow renders inside iframe

    Note over Learner,JWKS: Phase 3 — Deep Linking (optional — content selection)

    Learner->>ExtLMS: Teacher clicks "Select content"
    ExtLMS->>SetFlow: POST /api/lti/deep-link<br/>JWT with content_items URL
    SetFlow-->>Learner: SetFlow lists available resources
    Learner->>SetFlow: Selects resources
    SetFlow->>SetFlow: lti13-deep-link.ts<br/>Sign JWT response with LtiToolKey
    SetFlow-->>ExtLMS: Signed content items JWT (auto-form-post)
    ExtLMS->>ExtLMS: Saves deep link resource (Lti13ResourceLink)

    Note over Learner,JWKS: Phase 4 — Grade Passback (AGS)

    Learner->>SetFlow: Submits assignment inside iframe
    SetFlow->>SetFlow: lti13-grade-passback.ts<br/>getServiceAccessToken() (client_credentials JWT)
    SetFlow->>ExtLMS: POST score to platform AGS endpoint<br/>{ lineitem, score, userId, timestamp }
    ExtLMS->>ExtLMS: Grade recorded in external LMS gradebook
